{"id": "1497100670518562816", "channel_id": "1497100670518562816", "type": 0, "author_id": "105610060087996416", "author_name": "ican", "author_bot": false, "content": "After you reset the event shop often enough that the limited items are gone, this warning serves no purpose anymore. If people didn't read it the first 5 times it was displayed, they won't read it afterwards either and still wonder why their limited items won't refresh.\nSo after all shop refreshes are used, that message should not display. I would even suggest to just auto-refresh when all items are gone or let me turn in my whole currency stack in one go.\n\nIt's a slight inconvenience, but it's probably easy to fix and it will feel just right to have fewer steps to turn in stuff after you pressed the single turn in button often enough.", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T05:03:34.637000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1497100671076270100", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 112360, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1497100670518562816/1497100671076270100/image.png?ex=69ec4b26&is=69eaf9a6&hm=f26344978f08d8a42e6fbb7c5eab4ae9b2d48f303417ed9a381aa6e4dcb21a4a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1497100670518562816", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Do not display Shop-Reset Warning if it no longer applies", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1497103748638445658", "channel_id": "1497023046496813097", "type": 0, "author_id": "141021087747145728", "author_name": "smile.__", "author_bot": false, "content": "This is kinda funny because `1%` is technically, `0.01`, so `0.25%` is in fact, `0.0025%`\n\nBut it is possible the equation is wrong, yes.", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T05:15:48.518000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-24T05:18:20.593000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1497023046496813097", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Question about Arachnes E1 scaling calcs", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1497104624312647740", "channel_id": "1497023046496813097", "type": 19, "author_id": "693905974750216212", "author_name": "fishhazardthewizard", "author_bot": false, "content": "i think the main point fjant is trying to get at is the 25% bonus not being added directly to the initial 75% boost, but rather the rm boost only affecting the 25% bonus, rather than being its own boost\n\nthe first equation is ``24 * 0.25%`` so it's not a difference between the % value calcs", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T05:19:17.295000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["141021087747145728"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1497103748638445658", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1497023046496813097", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Question about Arachnes E1 scaling calcs", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168893200044183"]}
