{"id": "1497108041135427595", "channel_id": "1497023046496813097", "type": 0, "author_id": "141021087747145728", "author_name": "smile.__", "author_bot": false, "content": "+0.5 from Covenant Piece, +12 from half-Covenant, +36, from Wheel 1, +18 from Wheel 2, effect is +30%, and +15% from Pursuit\n\n12+36+18, -> 66.5RM\n\nExalting gives +25%, the bonus should be +66*.025, = 16.5%\n\nTotal bonus is then 41.5%, on top of the base.\n\nBut the thing that I'm not understanding, is my Exalt skill is 98, but this isn't in game, it's on the Awakener page, so it shouldn't be calculated as such.\n\nSo it may be that the tooltip itself is wrong.", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T05:32:51.929000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-24T05:33:02.343000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1497108040934232217", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 105110, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1497023046496813097/1497108040934232217/image.png?ex=69ec5203&is=69eb0083&hm=f3cde6720b1580cc2a4bc3cea770e17f0aadb098c655fb0539c4b64fc516032d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1497023046496813097", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Question about Arachnes E1 scaling calcs", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168893200044183"]}
